                <p>
                    A few years ago the idea was born to found a European Society for surgeons who specialize in
                    rhinoplasty analog to the 1996 founded U.S. Rhinoplasty Society.
                    Therefore a group of nine surgeons (plastic surgeons and otorhinolaryngologists) from Europe founded
                    in May 2011 the Rhinoplasty Society of Europe in Stuttgart, Germany. The Rhinoplasty Society of
                    Europe, is intended as a scientifical and educational platform for plastic surgeons,
                    otorhinolaryngologists and maxillofacial surgeons who are deeply committed to plastic,
                    reconstructive and aesthetic nasal surgery.</p>

                <p>The first formal congress was after the 20th Anniversary Advanced Course for Functional and
                    Aesthetic Rhinoplasty in Stuttgart, Germany in April of 2012, at which the first President, Prof.
                    Dr. med. Dr. med. habil Wolfgang Gubisch, presided.
                </p>
