                    the court, but changed the name into „Rhinoplasty Society of Europe“. Approval of the constitution
                    and the bylaws including changing the name, installation of the board. The constitution of the board
                    demonstrates this society as an open one for all who are interested, independent of their
                    speciality.</p>

